column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.modelMag_g,extinction_g,p.modelMag_i,extinction_i, expAB_i, t.tmassxsc_ra, t.tmassxsc_dec, t.J_BA,t.K_R_EFF,t.K_MNSURFB_EFF, t.R_EXT,t.J_M_EXT,t.J_MSIG_EXT,t.H_M_EXT,t.H_MSIG_EXT, t.K_M_EXT,t.K_MSIG_EXT,t.K_R_EFF,t.K_MNSURFB_EFF FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN TwoMassXSC t ON p.objID = t.objID ORDER BY x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
